<../../../index.trig> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#8acb9687d181e54828dee2dfed029797>.
<#8acb9687d181e54828dee2dfed029797> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Create>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/HERA>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#published> "2026-04-14T17:12:11.578Z"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>.
<#8acb9687d181e54828dee2dfed029797> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/HERA> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Organ za pripravljenost in odzivanje na izredne zdravstvene razmere"@sl, "Autoritatea pentru Pregătire și Răspuns în caz de Urgență Sanitară"@ro, "Autoridade de Preparação e Resposta a Emergências Sanitárias"@pt, "Myndigheden for Kriseberedskab og -indsats på Sundhedsområdet"@da, "Awtorità għat-Tħejjija u għar-Rispons f’Każ ta’ Emerġenza tas-Saħħa"@mt, "Veselības ārkārtas situāciju gatavības un reaģēšanas iestāde"@lv, "Tervisealasteks hädaolukordadeks valmisoleku ja neile reageerimise asutus"@et, "Орган за готовност и реакция при извънредни здравни ситуации"@bg, "Terveyshätätilanteiden valmiusviranomainen"@fi, "Autorità per la preparazione e la risposta alle emergenze sanitarie"@it, "Urząd ds. Gotowości i Reagowania na Stany Zagrożenia Zdrowia"@pl, "Tijelo za pripravnost i odgovor na zdravstvene krize"@hr, "Myndigheten för beredskap och insatser vid hälsokriser"@sv, "Health Emergency Preparedness and Response Authority"@en, "Egészségügyi Szükséghelyzet-felkészültségi és -reagálási Hatóság"@hu, "An tÚdarás um Ullmhacht agus Freagairt i dtaca le hÉigeandálaí Sláinte"@ga, "Αρχή Ετοιμότητας και Αντιμετώπισης Καταστάσεων Έκτακτης Υγειονομικής Ανάγκης"@el, "Pasirengimo ekstremaliosioms sveikatos situacijoms ir reagavimo į jas institucija"@lt, "Autoriteit voor paraatheid en respons inzake noodsituaties op gezondheidsgebied"@nl, "Autorité de préparation et de réaction en cas d’urgence sanitaire"@fr, "Úrad pre pripravenosť a reakcie na núdzové zdravotné situácie"@sk, "Úřad pro připravenost a reakci na mimořádné situace v oblasti zdraví"@cs, "Autoridad de Preparación y Respuesta ante Emergencias Sanitarias"@es, "Behörde für die Krisenvorsorge und -reaktion bei gesundheitlichen Notlagen"@de;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Health Emergency Preparedness and Response Authority (HERA) is a European Commission service. Its core mission is to strengthen health security coordination within the Union during preparedness and crisis response times, and bringing together the Member States, the industry and the relevant stakeholders in a common effort; to address vulnerabilities and strategic dependencies within the Union related to the development, production, procurement, stockpiling and distribution of medical countermeasures; to contribute to reinforcing the global health emergency preparedness and response architecture."@en;
