    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Poradný výbor pre bezpečnosť, hygienu a ochranu zdravia pri práci"@sk, "Comité consultivo de seguridad, higiene y protección de la salud en el trabajo"@es, "Komitet Doradczy ds. Bezpieczeństwa, Higieny i Ochrony Zdrowia w Miejscu Pracy"@pl, "Det Rådgivende Udvalg for Sikkerhed, Hygiejne og Sundhedsbeskyttelse på Arbejdspladsen"@da, "Comitato consultivo per la sicurezza, l’igiene e la tutela della salute sul luogo di lavoro"@it, "Comité Consultivo para a Segurança, Higiene e Proteção da Saúde no Local de Trabalho"@pt, "Työturvallisuuden, työhygienian ja työterveyshuollon neuvoa-antava komitea"@fi, "Advisory Committee on Safety, Hygiene and Health Protection at Work"@en, "Raadgevend Comité voor de veiligheid, de hygiëne en de gezondheidsbescherming op de arbeidsplaats"@nl, "Beratender Ausschuss für Sicherheit, Arbeitshygiene und Gesundheitsschutz am Arbeitsplatz"@de, "Rådgivande kommittén för arbetarskyddsfrågor"@sv, "Συμβουλευτική επιτροπή για την ασφάλεια, την υγιεινή και την προστασία της υγείας στον τόπο εργασίας"@el, "Comité consultatif pour la sécurité, l’hygiène et la protection de la santé sur le lieu de travail"@fr, "Tööohutuse, tööhügieeni ja töötervishoiu nõuandekomitee"@et;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Committee had the task of assisting the Commission in the preparation and implementation of activities in the fields of safety, hygiene and health protection at work. This task covered all sectors of the economy except the mineral extracting industries falling within the responsibility of the Mines Safety and Health Commission and except the protection of the health of workers against the dangers arising from ionizing radiations which was subject to special regulations pursuant to the Treaty establishing the European Atomic Energy Community."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "ACSHHPW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001363"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "ACSHHPW"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "ACSHHPW"@en, "CCSHS"@pt, "CCSHS"@fr, "CCSHS"@es;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/ACSHHPW_1974_0>;
