    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Comité de Política Orçamental"@pt, "Comité de politique budgétaire"@fr, "Comitato di politica di bilancio"@it, "Budgetary Policy Committee"@en, "Eelarvepoliitika komitee"@et, "Comité voor begrotmgspolitiek"@nl, "Comité de política presupuestaria"@es, "Ausschuß für Haushaltspolitik"@de;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Committee studied and compared the broad lines of the budgetary policies of the Member States. The Opinion of the Committee could be obtained by the Council or by the Commission. Moreover, the Committee may, on its own initiative, delivered Opinions whenever it considers this necessary for the proper fulfilment of its task. The Committee consisted of representatives of the Member States and of the Commission."@en;
