<#8bcd4548ebc58bbc05471de1b9a31e41> {
<http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CINEA> a <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#Concept>;
    <http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/authority/deprecated> "false";
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Europeiska genomförandeorganet för klimat, infrastruktur och miljö"@sv, "Európai Éghajlat-politikai, Környezetvédelmi és Infrastrukturális Végrehajtó Ügynökség"@hu, "Agenzia esecutiva europea per il clima, l’infrastruttura e l’ambiente"@it, "Agence exécutive européenne pour le climat, les infrastructures et l’environnement"@fr, "Agenția Executivă Europeană pentru Climă, Infrastructură și Mediu"@ro, "An Ghníomhaireacht Feidhmiúcháin Eorpach um an Aeráid, Bonneagar agus Comhshaol"@ga, "Euroopa Kliima, Taristu ja Keskkonna Rakendusamet"@et, "Europska izvršna agencija za klimu, infrastrukturu i okoliš"@hr, "European Climate, Infrastructure and Environment Executive Agency"@en, "Európska výkonná agentúra pre klímu, infraštruktúru a životné prostredie"@sk, "Det Europæiske Forvaltningsorgan for Klima, Infrastruktur og Miljø"@da, "Evropska izvajalska agencija za podnebje, infrastrukturo in okolje"@sl, "Eiropas Klimata, infrastruktūras un vides izpildaģentūra"@lv, "Agencia Ejecutiva Europea de Clima, Infraestructuras y Medio Ambiente"@es, "Europees Uitvoerend Agentschap klimaat, infrastructuur en milieu"@nl, "Europos klimato, infrastruktūros ir aplinkos vykdomoji įstaiga"@lt, "Европейска изпълнителна агенция за климата, инфраструктурата и околната среда"@bg, "Ευρωπαϊκός Εκτελεστικός Οργανισμός για το Κλίμα, τις Υποδομές και το Περιβάλλον"@el, "L-Aġenzija Eżekuttiva Ewropea għall-Klima, għall-Infrastruttura u għall-Ambjent"@mt, "Europäische Exekutivagentur für Klima, Infrastruktur und Umwelt"@de, "Euroopan ilmasto-, infrastruktuuri- ja ympäristöasioiden toimeenpanovirasto"@fi, "Evropská výkonná agentura pro klima, infrastrukturu a životní prostředí"@cs, "Agência de Execução Europeia do Clima, das Infraestruturas e do Ambiente"@pt, "Europejska Agencja Wykonawcza ds. Klimatu, Infrastruktury i Środowiska"@pl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Climate, Infrastructure and Environment Executive Agency is entrusted with the implementation of the following (parts of) Union programmes: Innovation Fund; Connecting Europe Facility: Transport (including military mobility and the Cohesion Fund contribution) and Energy; Horizon Europe: Pillar II, cluster 5: Climate, energy and mobility; LIFE: Nature and biodiversity; Circular economy and quality of life; Climate change mitigation and adaptation; Clean energy transition; Renewable Energy Financing Mechanism; Public sector loan facility, under the Just Transition Mechanism; European Maritime, Fisheries and Aquaculture Fund (direct management) and compulsory contributions to Regional Fisheries Management Organisations (RFMOs) and other international organisations, as well as with the implementation of the legacy of the following (parts of) Union programmes: Connecting Europe Facility: Energy and Transport (including the Cohesion Fund contribution); Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal challenge 3: Secure, clean and efficient energy; Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal challenge 4: Smart, green and integrated transport; Horizon 2020: Part III: Societal challenge 5: Climate action, Environment, resource efficiency and raw materials; LIFE: Climate Action and Environment; European Maritime and Fisheries Fund."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "CINEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#PUB_CORP>, "10.2926"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#DOI_P>, "TENEA_CRF_232551"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>, "HZ"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#OP_CAT>, "9405"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#ISBN_RG>, "CINEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "CINEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001636"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "TENEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#WHOISWHO>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "CINEA"@ro, "CINEA"@ga, "CINEA"@sv, "CINEA"@pl, "CINEA"@hr, "CINEA"@fr, "CINEA"@fi, "CINEA"@bg, "CINEA"@mt, "CINEA"@en, "CINEA"@hu, "CINEA"@es, "CINEA"@et, "CINEA"@da, "CINEA"@lv, "CINEA"@de, "CINEA"@el, "CINEA"@it, "CINEA"@sl, "CINEA"@cs, "CINEA"@pt, "CINEA"@sk, "CINEA"@lt, "Cinea"@nl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/CINEA_2021_0>;
