    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Secretariaat-generaal van de EIB"@nl, "Secretariado-Geral do BEI"@pt, "Secrétariat général de la BEI"@fr, "EIP peasekretariaat"@et, "Az EBB főtitkársága"@hu, "EIB Ģenerālsekretariāts"@lv, "Ard-Rúnaíocht BEI"@ga, "Generalsekretariat der EIB"@de, "EIB generalinis sekretoriatas"@lt, "EIB’s Generalsekretariatet"@da, "Segretariato generale della BEI"@it, "EIB:s generalsekretariatet"@sv, "General Secretariat of the EIB"@en, "EIP:n pääsihteeristö"@fi, "Generálny sekretariát EIB"@sk, "Secretariatul general al BEI"@ro, "Segretarjat Ġenerali tal-BEI"@mt, "Generalni sekretariat EIB"@sl, "Glavno tajništvo EIB-a"@hr, "Generální sekretariát EIB"@cs, "Secretaría General del BEI"@es, "Генерален секретариат на ЕИБ"@bg, "Γενική Γραμματεία της ΕΤΕπ"@el, "Sekretariat generalny EBI"@pl;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The General Secretariat of the European Investment Bank (EIB) is responsible for implementing and monitoring the decision-making process and the provision of secretariat services for all the governing bodies in the Bank, defining institutional strategy (including the Corporate Operational Plan), providing economic analysis on the employment and growth impact of EIB activities and potential new products, coordinating and developing relations with EU institutions, international and development financing agencies and non-governmental organizations, communications and corporate responsibility. It also supervises the areas of Advisory Services as well as the Bank’s external offices."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EIB_SG"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "EIB_SG"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001546"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "General Secretariat of the European Investment Bank"@en, "Secrétariat général de la Banque européenne d’investissement"@fr;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EIB_SG_1958_0>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/identifier> "EIB_SG";
